node.text: As fitness junkies know, there’s no shortage of apps, livestreams and online workout videos these days. Nike’s Training Club app, for example, is currently offering its premium content free of charge. Its library of about 185 workouts feature bodyweight sessions, yoga classes and full-equipment workouts. If you’re gonna give some a go, let us know in the comments! 😊💪🏋️‍♀️🤸‍♂️🧘‍♂️#stayhome #stayhealthy #keepfit #fitness #health #healthylifestyle #Nike #NikeTraining #NikeTrainingClub #CNAluxury #CNAlifestyle (Pic: Nike Training Club)
Have been doing that since before the hairy C.B.
Not Tiger King, but Money Heist. Anyone else? 😂
